        "subject": "LU-12348 llite: enable \"flock\" mount option by default",
        "message": "LU-12348 llite: enable \"flock\" mount option by default\n\nBy default, flock()/lockf()/fcntl() functions that try to lock files\nwould return failure because \"-o flock\" option is not enabled by\ndefault. This would cause failure to applications which are being\nmigrated from other file systems to Lustre.\n\nThis patch enables \"flock\" option by default.\n\nChange-Id: Id6b8e8e26e8023d825fd74d6f6681649e965406c\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\n"
      },
